{"tid":2267141,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是靚早-光榮] 竟然太陽蛋唔係生嘅","createTime":"2020-11-02T00:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T02:52:15.000Z","uid":182895,"like":40,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65c713a216c23f879f7dab5355f793fcd6f8ba27","tid":2267141,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T00:43:55.000Z","msg":"由於尋日有<strong><span class=\"red\">幾百個美食家提點太陽蛋應該係生食</span></strong><br />\n所以今日抱住要食生蛋嘅心態去食早餐<br />\n今日食<span class=\"xx-large\">光榮</span><br />\n叫咗份沙嗲牛肉辛辣麵太陽蛋多士<br />\n叫完心諗死啦<br />\n唔記得好似琴日有啲人提我<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">要要求太陽蛋生熟程度</span></span></span></strong><br />\n不過算啦都叫咗啦<br />\n學啲人話齋食個<strong><span class=\"large\">$45</span></strong>嘅早餐學咩人有要求何況今日呢個早餐只係<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">$32</span></span><br />\n哇屌太陽蛋係冇生嘅蛋白, 蛋黃係生, 超輕微窿邊咬落口冇渣, 辛辣面唔使加錢, 好滿足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XaBQcJi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXaBQcJi.png&h=34b4cc47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bMTUWH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bMTUWH.png&h=212bb82f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91ec7c7690d1887382ff047a6cf8e1a0df04d313","tid":2267141,"uid":192465,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"渣家軍全面進場倒數10 9<br />\n我走先<br />\n呢度冇人頂住"},{"pid":"1314355e4eb2dd1ec6c387d017e578df1e300371","tid":2267141,"uid":67454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"91ec7c7690d1887382ff047a6cf8e1a0df04d313","tid":2267141,"uid":192465,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"渣家軍全面進場倒數10 9<br />\n我走先<br />\n呢度冇人頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T00:50:21.000Z","msg":"光榮咪又係渣家一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba23f8efab48e09e051188f570e52989b2c7220b","tid":2267141,"uid":254383,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8